If you can't see the plugin in the program it means two things:

1. It's somewhere else, try searching for element.aex and put it in Plug-in folder AE.

2. You need 32 bit version of Element (not cracked yet, not even the scene crack I think) or you can install windows 7 64 bit (useful to see more than 3 gb ram, I actually have 24...).
